    "role": "N/A",
    "person": "N/A",
    "content": "* President: A04 - Let’s move forward with the assumption that we will be able to use the space and make sure we have clear communication with the faculty to stay updated.\n* Maria: it’s been cleared out by eng outreach and should be good to use now\n* I understand UOSU has their deadlines from C&R but we will be able to work something out as long as we have made attempts to coordinate properly\n* It should be ready by the fall, but we can get a paper trail for this so that we can take it to them and ask for another room\n* We’re going to track the timeline for this\n* There aren’t any other rooms available that we can use for the whole week so we’re not sure what we’ll do if CBY A04 can’t be used\n* Internal: hiring\n* Just to clarify for those waiting to hire commissioners, you’ve already been sent the information of those who applied to be commissioners and you’re expected to conduct the hiring process for that\n* I’m only doing the Manager selection process\n* There’s two people who are interested in Secretary\n* Let me know if you need any clarification\n* We’re going to wait for next meeting for the Manager of External Awareness, because someone replied today with interest in doing an interview (the email had gone to spam)",
    "meeting_date": "2025-06-19",
    "meeting_date_display": "Jun 19, 2025"
  },
